<L>__{interior de lessepses' house. outside viola's bedroom. night.}
<A>__{the nurse, drags a chair a rocker outside the bedroom door, and takes up her position. she sits down, keeping guard. pretty soon there comes the regular creak of viola's bed. the nurse fans herself furiously with her little lacy fan. she crosses herself. a chambermaid comes along the gallery outside the bedroom door. she is dusting her way along. the chambermaid becomes aware of the regular creaking. she pauses. the nurse begins to rock in her chair, keeping time with the creaking from within. the chambermaid stares at the nurse. the nurse stares at the chambermaid.}
<C>__{nurse}
<D>__{go to, go to.}
